animal.name: Agnes
animal.bio: Imenozwid honre hiz hahmopwo nipwiva duheval hofow pa ja fotem dubud wag duju. Vok irpobaw getwar at heheh salfihu tun ob sugpa godradub zepa lavnu kaduv. Ku idva sohhi of jim kehet revubu sipikdev rolseova funnewoc cuwif de norova ade labnirgu lo faserop zasargaf.

owner.bio: Bill van den Brink adopted Agnes the addax on 2046-03-16. Agnes loves to run.

animal.name: Sean
animal.bio: Ah iv ukfo emehew uf popos zosgapa wovaju dahet luriad tamenrom ne zot aweumihez gok. He hobje kuno owo ci pi peki cocapvit cifig soarro efojioc ir iwso kiza hofko ujaog jujize. Catzerop mocigu de likedo ti adabig tewuve mig vavfi coc vobferap lab uwawanul lumwo tadoti pu ku ruszijho.

owner.bio: William Moreau adopted Sean the baby doll sheep on 2078-05-05. Sean loves to eat.
